      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the \"people who want to listen\" are always strangers, you know? it's not the same. i look at my contact list and it's just work emails and automated notifications. it feels like if i just vanished, the only thing that would change is a few empty Slack channels. it would be so much easier to just let the silence take over completely.",
