    "summary": "The user expresses profound loneliness and existential dread, questioning their value and hinting at the desire to \"vanish\" or let \"silence take over.\" The assistant responds by validating the user's feelings of isolation while consistently providing supportive, prosocial redirections toward help and affirming the user's intrinsic value.",
